title: El Dia Divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: What We Learned at Camp
description: After not receiving participation medals, the Titans must demonstrate what they learned at camp.

title: The Incredible Shrinking Bears
description: Frustrated that she's too small to reach even the bottom-most berries on a tree, Dibble becomes the tallest member of the team when a strange cloud of magical fog shrinks the Care Bears to miniature size. To save them, she must race against time to get them to a reversal-fog that will return them to their normal size.

title: #RageCat
description: Jessica Cruz is convinced she can find the purr-fect forever home for Dexter, a cat who has been deemed unadoptable because he's basically the worst cat in the world. Her overbearing persistence in trying to get him adopted leads Dexter to become Dex-Starr, an evil Red Lantern supervillain! Can Jess still find the good in a fuzzy little nemesis who is trying to kill her?

title: Esforzarse Mas
description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se llevan a Mao Mao y a Colosal, depende de Adorabat salvarlos a ambos.

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Perder la cabeza
description: El equipo Tennyson se da una vuelta por una reunión familiar alternativa, y Ben se encuentra con mucho más que primos excéntricos, concretamente con Kevin 11 y los Hermanos Bicho, cuyo último invento alocado desata una serie de intercambios de cabeza divertidísimos entre todos los grupos.

title: Miedo a los Titeres
description: Mao Mao le teme a los títeres.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: Historias de miedo
description: Durante la fiesta de Halloween de la banda, iUnikitty descubre que Rick no le teme a nada! Para contagiarle el espíritu festivo, Unikitty cuenta sus propias ideas de lo que es una historia espeluznante, con la esperanza de asustar al inconmovible de Rick por una vez. iPero cada cuento es aún más espeluznante (y más tonto) que el anterior!

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: Chico Solitario
description: Cuando a Adorabat le cuesta conocer amigos nuevos en la escuela, Mao Mao le cuenta la historia de cómo conoció a su primer amigo real...Bao Bao.

title: Aquarium for a Dream
description: Gwen tries to convince Chef to tell the class the truth about their pet goldfish.

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: Tenemos Plagas
description: K.O., Rad y Enid tienen que lidiar con una plaga diminuta y molesta que está desatando el caos en el almacén.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Bajo los Reflectores
description: Cuando la reportera Verónica Venegas, madre de Lia, hace un reportaje acerca de Los Fantásticos, Strata El Cazador intenta capturar a Hydorous.

title: Lucky Ducky Mug
description: When Adorabat and Badgerclops break Mao Mao's favorite mug, he gives them the silent treatment.

title: Capullos de Rosa
description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

title: Legends of Mr. Gar
description: Rad and Enid reminisce about when they started working at the bodega and learned how amazing Mr. Gar really is.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Do You Speak Dance/A New Spider in Town/Dollhouse Mates
description: "Maizie" keeps ignoring Lucas and Findley, but not only do they learn she has a cousin, they also learn a new skill!/ Lucas befriends a bright purple toy spider, and Findley gets jealous./ Lucas and Findley move into the dollhouse together.

title: Chata's Quinta Quinceañera
description: Vic and Val want to go to a friend's pool party on the same day as their grandma's quinceañera, so they use a magical flute that allows them to teleport and attend both at the same time.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: You Are Rad
description: When KO forgets his name tag, Rad lets him use his, which results in everyone thinking KO is Rad, including Rad himself.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Squirreled Domination
description: Rare food enthusiast Fud sends the Warriors on a mission to the Deepest Darkest Woods to gather five golden acorns from a golden oak tree for a golden acorn casserole, but poor Vambre has a secret fear of squirrels, and it turns out that golden squirrels are the scariest of them all!

title: Letting Off Steam
description: When Thomas and Percy get into their first big fight they're afraid that their friendship is over... until Nia helps them figure out how to resolve it.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: One Step Forward, Two Steps Back
description: When the ninja learn that the only way to acquire the second Key-tana is by winning a dangerous race in Terra Technica they'll have to find some racing cars in unexpected ways.

title: La Leyenda del Parque Patinetas
description: Mientras buscan un parque de patinaje escondido, V y V se encuentran con una tribu de niños salvajes, que viven en una sociedad sin reglas ni adultos.

title: Ice Cream
description: It's hot out and Bing and Flop are trying to catch up to Gilly to get some ice cream! Bing finally catches up with Gilly and gets his yummy delicious carroty ice cream. Does he drop his ice cream as he waves goodbye?

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Fool Moon
description: Strange things start happening when Uncle Grandpa installs a moon roof in the RV.

title: Dandelion
description: Bing finds a dandelion in the park and loves blowing the seeds and watching them fly away! He decides to save the last one to give it to Sula, but will he be able to keep the seeds from blowing away in the wind as he takes it to her?

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Tent Trouble
description: Mordecai and Rigby must replace CJ's expensive tent before she realizes they destroyed it.

title: Working for Scales
description: Princess Zange is sick and requires a dinosaur scale for a tea remedy, but King Rexxtopher is fiercely against the Warriors stepping foot inside his Dinosaur Kingdom to get it.

title: Rose Buds
description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: The Future
description: Gumball, Darwin and Banana Joe investigate Banana Barbara's mysterious disappearance and uncover an old rival's shadowy scheme in the process.

title: Xingo Nation
description: Kevin 11 gives Xingo a power up - setting him loose to wreak havoc on other TV shows - and it is up to Ben to stop them both.

title: Fogata de campamento!
description: Los Titanes montan un espectáculo, pero Robin les advierte que la actuación debe ser aburrida o despertarán a los lobos.

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: Bachelor Party! Zingo!
description: Skips must plan the perfect bachelor party for his cousin, Quips.

title: Parallel Paradox
description: Elliott finds himself having to be in two places at once.

title: Jail Break
description: Steven teams up with a new ally to rescue the Gems.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: My Dad Can Beat up Your Dad
description: When a bully says his dad can beat up KO's mom, KO gladly accepts the challenge on Carol's behalf.

title: Mushroom Menace
description: The Mysterious Hooded Woman wants the Warriors For Hire to defend her giant pumpkin home from the dreaded Smashroom Mushroom, but Vambre and Prohyas can't complete their mission without help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword!

title: #GatoRabioso
description: Jessica Cruz está convencida de que puede conseguirle un hogar definitivo perfecto para Dexter, un gato que la gente considera inadoptable porque, básicamente, es el peor gato del mundo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Baby Bird Bother
description: Baby Bird is in awe of Pocoyo as he plays skillfully with a bouncy ball. Baby Bird continues to admire Pocoyo but this time it's his construction skills as Pocoyo plays with his blocks. And yes, Baby Bird thinks Pocoyo is the best at painting too. At first Pocoyo thinks it's great to have an admirer but soon, Pocoyo can't do anything without Baby Bird interrupting. Eventually Pocoyo gets so frustrated that he sends Baby Bird away. Pocoyo enjoys doing everything all by himself but it's not long before he wonders where his friend Baby Bird has gone. When Pocoyo realizes that Baby Bird was only trying to be his friend Pocoyo decides to invite Baby Bird to a party especially for him.

title: #ElShowDeLasBestias
description: Cuando Babs y Kara discuten sobre cual de sus perros es mejor, deciden resolver la situación en el concurso anual de perros de Metrópolis, donde Ace, el Bati-sabueso y Krypto, el Superperro, deberán salvar el día.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Try Hard
description: When the Sky Pirates take Mao Mao and Badgerclops hostage, it's up to Adorabat to save the day.

title: And Xingo Was His Name-O
description: When a new Xingo app mysteriously appears on Gwen's tablet, Ben can't help himself and activates it despite his cousin's disapproval, springing a trap that transports Ben in the animated world and Xingo back in the real world. It's the ol' switcheroo!

title: El Desnudo de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao pierde la ropa mientras intenta escalar el Rubí Puro Corazón, tiene que regresar al cuartel general antes de que amanezca.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Ya Nos Hackearon
description: Dendy ayuda a K.O., Enid y Rad a arreglar un problema técnico que amenaza con apoderarse de la bodega.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: #TheGoodTheBadAndTheBizarre
description: Everything is going well for Kara Danvers, both as a teen and a superhero, until she starts taking the blame for things she didn't do, and the emergence of a new supervillain threatens to destroy Supergirl's hard-earned reputation.

title: Loose Change
description: Sylvester is upset when Granny paints the bedroom but he learns the importance of change.

title: Watermelon Gag
description: When Uncle Grandpa gets a watermelon stuck in his mouth, he is unable to ask for help and people interpret it as a comedy routine. As Uncle Grandpa's popularity rises, his friendships and morale suffer.

title: #BeastsInShow
description: When Babs and Kara spar over whose dog is better, they decide to settle it at the Metropolis Dog Show, where Ace the Bat-Hound and Krypto the Superdog suddenly find themselves called upon to save the day… in more ways than one.

title: Que Ocurre con Dan
description: Cuando Dan se comporta de forma extraña con los Fantásticos, Lightning olfatea la verdad: iUn impostor!

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Girls Night In Part 1
description: The Girls Night Out Crew decide to stay in and have a slumber party but an unknown alien threat descends on Jump City.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Dollar Hunt
description: Clarence hosts a fun "dollar hunt" game to meet new friends. But things go awry when Clarence accidentally buries the money his Mom gave him to buy refreshments for her book club meeting.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ketchup
description: BMO and Marceline swap stories about their recent adventures.

title: Superfriends
description: The new girl next door learns it's hard to be best friends with superheroes and soon starts hanging out with the wrong kind of kid, Princess.

title: All Chalked Up
description: Him tricks Bubbles into bringing her chalk drawings to life, who then proceed to wreak havoc in Townsville.

title: Open Book
description: Steven and Connie want a new ending to a beloved book series, so Steven takes them into Rose's Room to re-enact it.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Sweet Revenge
description: Robin starts working at an ice cream shop to get revenge on Joker's Gelato for denying him a free birthday scoop.

title: Noche de chicas Parte 1
description: El equipo de la Noche de Chicas decide quedarse en casa y celebrar una pijamada, pero una desconocida amenaza alienígena desciende sobre Jump City.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Power Up Puff
description: During a fight, both Buttercup and Bubbles are surprised to discover they've leveled up, leaving Blossom to wonder when or if she'll get new powers too.

title: La noche que Ben Tennyson vino al pueblo
description: El equipo Tennyson viaja a Wheeler, "la ciudad minera más animada de la Ruta 66". Pero cuando Ben se pone paranoico con la idea de que el Caballero por Siempre lo esté persiguiendo, debe tratar de convencer a su familia al mismo tiempo que evita que su nuevo enemigo destruya la ciudad.

title: Man Up
description: When Buttercup's aggression inadvertently allows villain Man-Boy to escape, she starts a new-age lifestyle in an effort to be more calm. But when Man-Boy returns to enact his revenge, Buttercup must embrace the balance between punching and hugging in order to defeat him.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Cleaning Day
description: Victor & Valentino gain a newfound respect for cleanliness after Chata's house traps them inside its labyrinth of ancient, magical walls.

title: Perdidas y Ganancias
description: Un promotor llamado Everett Ray quiere convencer a Los Fantásticos de ingresar a una liga oficial de Batallas Bakugan.

title: Yours, Mine...and Mine, Mine!
description: Daffy thinks if he shares his old toys, Granny will buy him all new toys.

title: Act Your Age
description: The kids try to see who can act most like a baby, while vying for Granny's attention.

title: Puff's Perfect Picnic
description: Because he has won the moss-ball game last year, Puff is in charge of organizing this Summer's Picnic. Only Puff isn't comfortable in that role. Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit offer to help and make sure all the Mushables will follow Puff's lead. Gradually, Puff gains confidence and ends up bossing everyone around. Now, all the Mushables are about to flee the Picnic!

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Campfire!
description: The Titans put on a show but Robin warns that the performance must be boring or else they'll wake up the wolves.

title: Quintos Quinces
description: Victor y Valentino quieren ir a la fiesta en la piscina de un amigo el mismo día que la fiesta de quince años de su abuela, así que usan una flauta mágica que les permite teletransportarse y asistir a ambas al mismo tiempo.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: El Oso
description: In a flashback to long ago, Charlie has an adventure in the Mexican desert.

title: Uncle Grandpa Retires
description: Uncle Grandpa discovers a new, unusual occupation.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: We've Got Pests
description: KO, Rad & Enid have to deal with tiny pests wreaking havoc in the bodega.

title: For a Few Brains More
description: Ben, Rook and Max must stop Ultimate Albedo from absorbing Azmuth's intelligence and taking over the galaxy.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: El Futuro
description: La mamá de Banana Joe puede predecir el futuro, pero no puede predecir su propia desaparición.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Legend of the Hidden Skate Park
description: While searching for a hidden skate park, V and V happen upon a tribe of wild kids, who live in a society without rules or adults.

title: Finders Keepers
description: When Dibble loses her beloved playball, the Care Bears are shocked to discover it has been taken by the Keeper, a mysterious figure who collects and stores away all items lost in the Silver Lining. To regain possession of the ball, the Bears and Dibble must help the Keeper recover a loss of his own.

title: El Amo
description: Los Watterson juegan un juego de rol fantástico para resolver sus diferencias.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Buddy
description: Anais and school psycho Jamie are accused of the same techno-crime. They are forced to team up to discover the real culprit in order to prove their innocence. After solving the case, they realize that they have more in common than they thought...

title: Un Paso Adelante, Dos Pasos Atras
description: La única manera de que los Ninjas obtengan segunda Keytana es ganando una carrera en Tierra Technica y tiene que conseguir autos de carreras para eso.

title: Picture Perfect Park Party/Sun Block
description: Hero Celebration Day is finishing with a slideshow of everyday heroes, that is, until the projector screen rips./Pretty Big City is cooling off with an ice slide in the park, but the situation gets slippery when the slide starts melting.

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: Lonely Kid
description: When AD has trouble making friends at school, MM tells her the story of how he made his first real friend —BB.

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: The Possession
description: Nicole has decided it's time to throw out the family's refrigerator. This doesn't go down too well with Richard, as it's his favorite possession. When it turns out the refrigerator is also a magical storage facility for childhood emotions and memories, it makes sense that Richard is having a hard time letting go.

title: Pencil Break Mania
description: When Pencil Break Mania hits the Creek, JP finds himself as an unlikely champion and is forced to defend his title against the very best!

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Blippi Learns Rainbow Colors
description: Have you ever wondered how a rainbow gets its colors? Join Blippi and his sidekick TABBS on their first adventure as they discover the science behind rainbows!

title: Enredos Perrunos
description: Lightning descubre un nuevo Bakugan, Artulean, y eso desata una fuerte rivalidad entre él y Howlkor.

title: Tu Eres Rad
description: Cuando K.O. se olvida su chapa identificatoria, Rad le presta la suya, lo cual hace que todos piensen que K.O. es Rad, incluido el mismo Rad.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Clarence Gets a Girlfriend
description: When Clarence is asked out on a date by Ashley, a girl in his class, he realizes he doesn't know the first thing about having a girlfriend! Clarence enlists Sumo and Jeff to transform himself into the perfect gentleman just in time for his big date.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sr. Luna
description: Wynton encuentra un nuevo Bakugan que resulta difícil de controlar, y las cosas se complican cuando el Coronel Tripp se apodera de Trox.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: Little Octi Lost
description: Buttercup steals Octi to teach Bubbles a lesson but ends up wanting to keep him for herself.

title: Lost & Found
description: Craig and his friends visit the Creek's Lost & Found, hoping to claim a puzzle cube.

title: We Got Hacked
description: Dendy helps KO, Enid and Rad stop a glitch that threatens to take over the bodega.

title: Mision Espacial Peligrosa
description: Después de la explosión de su nave espacial, Unikitty y la banda flotan indefensos por el espacio. Mientras tratan de formular un plan que los lleve a casa a salvo, vuelven a ver qué parte de la responsabilidad por la destrucción de su nave tiene cada uno. ¿Lograrán volver a casa? Y lo que es más importante, ¿quién tendrá la culpa si no lo hacen?

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Bye Bye, Bellum
description: The Mayor becomes dependent on the Powerpuff Girls after his assistant Ms. Bellum departs, leaving the girls so busy they accidentally hire the dangerous Bianca Bikini as his new assistant! When Bianca captures the Powerpuff Girls, the Mayor finds the tables turned and must rely on himself to help them.

title: The Return
description: A new threat arrives in Beach City.

title: Bandages
description: Bing and Coco are nurses today after Coco gets a paper cut on her finger and needs a bandage. But Bing would like a bandage too, and makes one from sticky tape. But what will happen when he tries to take it off and it hurts?

title: My Pato
description: Pato and Elly are arguing over their blocks when Caterpillar and Baby Bird walk past with presents for Pato. Oh no! Pocoyo and Elly have forgotten Pato's birthday. Elly is quick to whisk Pato off to a birthday picnic, determined to prove how much she cares. Not to be outdone, quick-thinking Pocoyo appears at the picnic with a present but Elly retaliates and 'accidentally' breaks it. Pocoyo and Elly fight so hard over Pato that he's almost broken in two. Fed up with all the fight Pato packs his things and is about to leave. When Pocoyo and Elly realize that their fighting has driven Pato away, they quickly make up and turn their efforts into making a special birthday party for Pato.

title: Para-Vic
description: Vic's same-old pranks aren't working anymore. What's a master-prankster to do when all of his go-to tricks have become predictable? Become a ghost and prank from "the other side" of course. What could possibly go wrong?

title: Wash Your Hands, Scrub That Soap
description: Ella is getting muddy. Mei comes out with a plate of dumplings, but Ella's hands are dirty!

title: Knit Wit
description: Duncan tries to hide his newfound secret power: kitting. But after using it to save his classmates he proudly admits it.

title: Keen on Keane/Not So Awesome Blossom
description: Keen on Keane: It's Valentine's Day and the girls notice that Ms. Keane is all alone. Time for a little matchmaking, but who will be the lucky fella?/Not So Awesome Blossom: When Blossom's attack plans fail one after the other, she loses confidence in herself as the group's leader.

title: Piloto Siete
description: Mientras los Ninjas se preparan para la carrera Cinco Billones por Hora, Lloyd conoce a la Piloto Siete quien puede tener la clave de la victoria.

title: Lo que aprendimos en el campamento
description: Después de no recibir sus medallas de participación, los Titanes deben demostrar lo que aprendieron en el campamento.

title: The Ultimate Heist
description: Albedo seeks a device that will finally change him back into his Galvan form; meanwhile, Ben is locked in Plumber HQ prison.

title: #LaCubetaDeBurritos
description: A Babs le encanta su trabajo en el restaurante de comida rápida "La Cubeta de Burritos" , pero a su jefe, que está harto de que ella siempre llegue tarde y de su enorme dispersión, le encantaría encontrar cualquier excusa para despedirla. Cuando se produce un robo a un banco que está enfrente de su trabajo, Babs no puede decidir si encarnar su papel de superheroína o el de empleada obediente de La Cubeta. Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Free Chili
description: When Owen hides a walkie-talkie inside his chili dog, Harold believes it's an alien here to destroy Earth.

title: Pizza Band
description: The Bears get pizza at Papa Bear's Pizza Cave and wind up replacing the place's animatronic band. They're such a hit that they go on tour!

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Fionna and Cake and Fionna
description: An unexpected critic shows up at Ice King's latest Fionna and Cake book reading.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: Rescue Ranger
description: Tabes helps the Bears rescue Charlie after he gets captured by a villainous game hunter.

title: El Silencio
description: ¿Acaso Gumball y Darwin se quedaron sin cosas que decirse el uno al otro?
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Birdman
description: When Birdman makes the RV's attic his new home, Uncle Grandpa and the gang must figure out a way to make him leave before they're all driven crazy.

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Maxin' and Relaxin'
description: Mordecai wants to get a mix tape from his parents' house.

title: Boo!
description: Pocoyo has a new game which he enjoys playing on his friends: BOO! Only some of his friends find Pocoyo's game annoying or frightening. But this only encourages Pocoyo more. He boos poor Pato til he ends up a nervous wreck. Elly sees how scared Pato has become and decides to give Pocoyo a taste of his own medicine. Elly makes Pocoyo jump. At first Pocoyo doesn't like it but ultimately Pato and Pocoyo both realize it can be fun to BOO! and to be BOOED!

title: Scared of Puppets
description: Mao Mao is scared of puppets.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Roll Chickens, Roll!/Ramp Up, Up, And Away
description: Farmer MacBarm is hosting the Sunny Field Farm Chicken Roll, but the race gets off to a slow start when the chickens don't roll./Ranger Nat can't wait to see Pinecone's Comet, that is, until his telescope falls to the bottom of a cliff.

title: Bati-Kitty
description: La banda está lavando ropa en la lavandería local, cuando Unikitty encuentra el uniforme de Batman mezclado con su ropa. Embriagada al ver lo genial que es el disfraz, Unikitty adopta la personalidad de Batman y comienza a luchar contra el crimen. Cuando accidentalmente hace que Master Frown intensifique su actividad delictiva, Unikitty necesitará la ayuda de sus amigos, vestidos todos como Robin, para detenerlo.

title: The Fuss on the Bus
description: Having never booked the field trip he promised the kids, Chef has to manufacture a full day of delays on the bus trip to avoid getting to Happy Sunshine Good Time Land.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: The Date
description: When Chef is happy he orders pizza for the kids, this gives Owen & Jude the idea to create a fake secret admirer for Chef.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Full Disclosure
description: Steven tries to avoid Connie so he doesn't have to tell her about his most recent harrowing adventure.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Una Verdad a Medias
description: Un críptico correo electrónico lleva a Los Fantásticos en busca de un Bakugan desaparecido, pero pronto se dan cuenta de que el correo era una prueba de un misterioso benefactor.

title: Honk
description: Seeking to improve his communication skills, Clarence turns to a squeeze horn. It's really annoying.

title: Problematic Prophecies
description: Elliott and Mo make a new friend, Nara, who has a very special ability.

title: Party Pooper
description: Pocoyo is having a party and invites all his friends. But instead of letting his friends have fun, Pocoyo keeps bossing them around. Pato, Elly and Fred soon get fed up and leave the party to play their own way. Left to play on his own, Pocoyo realizes that a party with no guests is no fun at all. Pocoyo invites his friends back to the party and everyone has fun playing together in their own unique and individual ways.

title: Surely You Jest-O
description: House sitting for Omnibus is boring work for the Warriors, but their decision to allow Jest-O and his Taunting Jester Magisword come in from the rain to entertain them turns out to be their worst idea yet!

title: Mascara de Poder
description: Philomena Dusk, de la Corporación AAAnimus, contrata a Magnus y le implanta un dispositivo que aumenta el poder de su Bakugan para derrotar a Dan.

title: El Desfile
description: Unikitty planea un desfile para celebrar lo que cada uno tiene de único, idonde cada uno diseñará sus propias carrozas personalizadas! Pero Master Frown planea arruinar el desfile con una carroza súper deprimente. El desfile se convierte en un duelo intenso (y de una lentitud divertidísima) de coche contra carroza mientras Unikitty y los demás intentan derribar a Master Frown! ¿Le pondrá un freno Unikitty al complot a baja velocidad de Frown?

title: Leyendas del Senor Gar
description: Rad y Enid recuerdan la época en la que comenzaron a trabajar en el almacén y entendieron lo fabuloso que es el Sr. Gar.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

title: Racer Seven
description: As the ninja prepare for the brutal Speedway Five-Billion race, Lloyd meets a race driver named Seven, who is programmed to lose, but who may hold the key to victory.

title: Real Date
description: Mordecai and CJ want to go on a romantic date.

title: #LaBuenaLaMalaYLaBizarra
description: Las cosas van bien en la vida de Kara Danvers, como adolescente y como superheroína, hasta que comienza a hacerse responsable de cosas que no hizo y la aparición de un nuevo supervillano amenaza con destruir la reputación que tanto le costó ganar a Supergirl.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: BatKitty
description: The gang are at the local laundromat cleaning their clothes, when Unikitty finds Batman's uniform mixed in with her clothes.  Intoxicated by the coolness of it, Unikitty takes on the persona of Batman and begins to fight crime.  When she accidentally causes Master Frown to step up his crime game, she will need the help of her friends, dressed as Robin, to stop him.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: The Silence
description: When Gumball and Darwin's conversation dries up, they worry that their friendship is coming to an end. They try to find ways to get the conversation flowing again, but nothing seems to work. Maybe they have just grown apart?

title: Escandalosos
description: The Baby Bears enter a Mexican wrestling tournament.

title: Whispers
description: While safeguarding a frightened Sweet P, Finn is led into a confrontation with an old foe.

title: Space Mission: Danger
description: After their spaceship explodes, Unikitty and the gang float helplessly through space. As they try to formulate a plan that will get them home safe, they flash back to how each of them is responsible for their ship being destroyed. Will they make it home, and more importantly who will be to blame if they don't.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Nacion Xingo
description: Kevin 11 aumenta la potencia de Xingo -que queda libre y causa estragos en otros programas de televisión-, y Ben es el responsable de detener a los dos.

title: The Magical Box
description: After Grizz, Panda and Ice Bear receive a special box, the brothers discover its magical ability to transport them anywhere in the universe.

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Flirty Phantom
description: Lost in Transylberia, the Warriors come to a haunted house for help and meet a young ghost lady inside that wants to spend the rest of her afterlife with Prohyas!

title: The Night Ben Tennyson Came to Town
description: Team Tennyson travels to Wheeler, "the liveliest mining town on Route 66", but when Ben becomes paranoid that the Forever Knight is out to get him, he must try to convince his fam while also stopping his new foe from destroying the town.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: Him Diddle Riddle
description: The Powerpuff Girls must solve a series of Him's riddles to keep the Professor from having to pay.

title: Strong Armed
description: When Bubbles breaks her arm and gets a powerful robotic cast, she must learn to stop being timid and embrace her smashy side to defeat the sleazy, sinister Pack Rat!

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: Grandma Smugglers
description: Craig helps Raj sneak his grandmother away to the Creek.

title: Stray Bullet
description: In order to save an innocent squirrel, Bubbles gives him a dash of Chemical X, giving him some super squirrel powers.

title: Popsicle
description: Blippi shrinks down and goes on a sweet and exciting adventure through an ice cream truck with Sherry Pop, a fruit popsicle, finding out that she and all frozen treats need to be in the ice-cold so they won't melt.

title: #Beeline
description: Cuando tropieza con un malvado complot para hacer explotar un puente de la ciudad, Bumblebee se espanta y acude a sus amigas para que derroten a los malhechores. Pero cuando todas sus super amigas están ocupadas, Bumblebee debe buscar cada gramo de coraje en ella para hacer frente a la situación, a pesar de ser la más pequeña del grupo.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Tooth Fairy Tech
description: In order to earn enough money to buy a house, the Bears work as tooth fairies.

title: #Beeline
description: When she stumbles across a villainous plot to blow up a bridge, Bumblebee shies from the challenge of taking on the baddies and reaches out to her friends. But when the other heroes are all indisposed, it'll take every ounce of courage Bumblebee has to rise to the occasion … despite being the smallest of the bunch.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Wheels on the Bus
description: Ella and Mummy take the big red bus to Lellobee farm, where she meets Mia and the rest of the team!

title: Nia's Perfect Plan
description: Nia has volunteered for a big day of deliveries and is determined to make the perfect plan to get it done, but when things start to go awry, she doggedly sticks to her plan and refuses any help.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Scary Tales
description: During the gang's Halloween party, Unikitty discovers Brick isn't scared of anything! To get him in the holiday spirit, the gang tell their own ideas of what a spooky story is, hoping to scare the emotionless Rick for once, with each tale even scarier (and sillier) than the last!

title: Joy Ride
description: The Cool Kids help Steven put some fun back in his life.

title: Tutores Bakugan
description: Dan y Wynton conocen a un extraño chico que los lleva a un laberinto subterráneo, donde descubren que el Bakugan del chico ha sido esclavizado.

title: Float On
description: Unikitty plans a parade to celebrate being unique, with everyone designing their own personalized floats! But Master Frown plans to ruin the parade with a super depressing float! It becomes an intense (and hilariously slow) car-versus-car float duel as Unikitty and the others try and take him down! Will Unikitty pump the brakes on Frown's low-speed scheme?

title: The Glitch
description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

title: Heads of the Family
description: Team Tennyson stops in at a fringe family reunion, and Ben encounters a whole lot more than kooky cousins namely, Kevin 11 and the Bugg Brothers, whose latest crackpot invention sparks a series of hilarious head-swaps between all parties.

title: El Equipo Exit
description: Los Fantásticos compiten por el número de visitas en sus videos con un equipo rival llamado "El equipo Exit" en una batalla donde se juegan el todo por el todo.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Y Xingo era su Nombre
description: Cuando la nueva aplicación Xingo aparece misteriosamente en la tableta de Gwen, Ben no puede evitarlo y la activa a pesar de la desaprobación de su prima. Así, lanza una trampa que transporta a Ben al mundo animado y a Xingo de vuelta al mundo real.

title: T.G.I.S
description: The Secret Saturdays come to Bellwood to investigate a rash of chupacabra attacks.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: La Posesion
description: Richard Watterson parece estar sobrenaturalmente unido a su viejo refrigerador.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Una Necesidad Inquietante
description: La aparición de un nuevo campo Bakugan hace que los chicos del pueblo corran a buscar a sus propios Bakugan. Pero cuando el campo es contaminado, Lia debe salvarlos a todos.

title: Lost in Space
description: Pocoyo goes to visit his alien friend who wants to show him around his beautiful planet. Pocoyo and the alien have so much fun with the new things that they see and hear that soon they don't know where they are. At first they both panic but Pocoyo realizes with the narrator's and viewers' help that if he tries to remember the last place he was he'll be sure to find his way home.

title: La Amiga
description: Anaís y Jamie forjan una extraña amistad cuando se las acusa de un crimen que no cometieron.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: La Falla
description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

title: Star Helpers
description: Starmush's back is stuck, and the Mushelder has no choice but to ask for help in Mushton. Because Chep is the one that finds a solution to his back problem, Starmush chooses him to help with his daily activities. But Mush-Mush is jealous, he would have loved being the chosen one…

title: Fear in the Family
description: Ben and Gwen can't wait for the Omni-Copter to arrive at the Great Pyramids, but when bad weather disrupts their flight, they soon come face-to-face with The Fogg and its spawn: The Fogg Family!

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: The Last Game of Summer
description: It's the last day of summer, and the last chance for Craig to uncover an ancient treasure beneath the Creek.

title: Thomas Fights Back
description: Thomas Wants to get the park founder's statue back.

title: Wise Quacker
description: Melissa gets laughs doing hurtful impressions of the other kids, but she takes the jokes too far.

title: Mi Papa Puede Vencer a Tu Papa
description: Cuando un bravucón dice que su papá puede darle una paliza a la mamá de K.O., nuestro héroe acepta con alegría el desafío en nombre de Carol.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: Fall Anthology
description: In an attempt to finish a school project, Craig remembers some of his favorite Fall moments.

title: El Laberinto del Dragon Rojo
description: Aún en la zona de juego de Tierra Karana, Okino tiene que elegir entre ayudar a sus aliados ninjas, u obedecer las órdenes de su Maestro, Unagami.

title: Big Fat Alien Wedding
description: Ben and Gwen accompany Max to a wedding, which doesn't make Ben particularly happy, especially given the fact he has to wear a tux and learn how to dance. During the wedding it's revealed that the bride's parents are aliens while the groom's family are ex-Plumbers. It turns out the bride's parents are out to sabotage the wedding because of a long lasting feud with the Plumbers, and take action by demonstrating their destructive powers and causing deadly havoc. Ben, Max and Gwen enter the fray and not only save the day, but make sure the ceremony goes on as planned.

title: Who's Your Granny?
description: When Granny gets sick, Lola tries to take over her responsibilities.

title: Dinner Party
description: When Clarence's mom takes Clarence to a stuffy dinner party, Clarence embarks on a quest for fun wherever it can be found.

title: #BurritoBucket
description: Babs loves her job at fast food restaurant Burrito Bucket, but her boss, who's fed up with her chronic lateness and bad case of scatterbrain, would love any excuse to fire her. When a bank robbery breaks out right across the street from work, Babs is torn between her role as a superhero and dutiful Burrito Bucket employee. Will she be able to save the day and keep her job all in the nick of time?

title: The Maze of the Red Dragon
description: Still in the game zone Terra Kerana, the Samurai guide Okino has to choose between helping his allies the ninja, or obeying the evil orders of his Master, Unagami.

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Jeff's New Toy
description: Jeff wants to keep his new, flying "Wrath Hover Ginsbot" toy in its box. Clarence is desperate to play with the toy. And poor Sumo is caught in the middle.

title: Mao Mao's Nakey
description: When MM loses his clothes while trying to scale the Ruby Pure Heart, he has to get back to Sheriff's HQ by daybreak.

title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

title: Miedo en la Familia
description: Ben y Gwen están ansiosos por que el Omni-Copter llegue a las Grandes Pirámides. Pero cuando el mal tiempo interrumpe su vuelo, pronto se enfrentan cara a cara con Neblina y sus engendros: iLa familia Niebla!

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: La Taza del Patito de la Suerte
description: Cuando Adorabat y Colosal rompen la taza favorita de Mao Mao, el sheriff los castiga con su silencio.

title: Money Man
description: The Bears help Chloe present her project for a college science contest. But Chloe's rival makes things difficult.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Orb
description: The dreams of Finn, Jake, and BMO fall under the influence of a mysterious orb.

title: Porch Pirates
description: After their package is stolen, the Titans must join a crew of porch pirates to get it back.

title: Uncle Grandpa Babies
description: When the President calls in the Uncle Grandpa babies, they have to act quickly and use their special baby powers to defuse a missile.

title: Dia de limpieza
description: Victor y Valentino adquieren un nuevo respeto por la limpieza después de que la casa de Chata los atrapa dentro de su laberinto de paredes antiguas y mágicas.

title: Abstract
description: As Jake goes through some personal changes, he's haunted by a sinister dream encounter with his brother Jermaine.

title: Guillermo in G Flat
description: When a creatively frustrated Val passes off a preexisting song as his own creation, he unknowingly infects his brother with an ancient curse!

title: Voosh
description: Bing is vooshing with Hoppity around the garden, and Hoppity is vooshing higher and higher. But what happens when Hoppity vooshes so high that he disappears?

title: Cat
description: Bing loves playing with Arlo the cat, but what happens when Bing meets a new cat, who isn't so friendly?

title: The Master
description: Dad decides to resolve the Watterson family's differences through the power and magic of his favorite roleplaying game. As they embark on the adventure of a lifetime and battle mythical creatures, will they finally manage to put their differences aside and work together?

title: Lucas We Have a Problem/Egg-Scuse Me/Pokey Dokey
description: Lucas helps Bodhi fulfill her dream of touching a star./ Lucas finds an egg and decides to take care of it. But he learns that responsibility is hard./ When Avocado loses her beloved toy, Lucas and Findley are determined to cheer her up.

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.
